title: Localization
description: The elements in HTMLKit are an abstraction of the elements in HTML (Hyper Text Markup Language). If you have written HTML before, then you know there are elements with or without an end tag. An element with an end tag will be represented in HTMLKit as an element with curly brackets, while an element without an end tag will be represented with round brackets.
